com.vmware.vapi.protocol.server.rpc

Interface RequestReceiver.RequestContext

  • Enclosing interface:
    RequestReceiver

    public static interface RequestReceiver.RequestContext
    Auxiliary (optional) information about the request which triggered the API invocation.

      • getAllProperties

        Map<String,String> getAllProperties()
        Gets a mapping between all incoming auxiliary property names as keys and their respective values.

        In case the underlying transport allows for multiple values per property (like the HTTP headers do), it is the implementation's responsibility to combine the values into a single String instance according to the transport's rules.

        Returns:
        map of all properties; never null
